---
import Layout from '../../Base.astro';
import SimpleHero from '../../components/SimpleHero.astro';
import FeaturedArticles from "../../components/FeaturedArticles.astro";
import ServicesRelatedWork from "../../components/ServicesRelatedWork.astro";
import "../../styles/pages/_services-list.scss";

---

<Layout
	title='Website Support & Maintenance'
	description='A website that never gets attention eventually turns into a liability. We provide ongoing support that keeps sites updated, stable, and usable after launch.'
>
	<SimpleHero tagline='Ongoing Support Services' title='Website Support' description="A website that never gets attention eventually turns into a liability. We provide ongoing support that keeps sites updated, stable, and usable after launch." lottieFile='website-support.json' />
	<div class='service-body'>
		<div class='wrapper wrapper--narrow'>
			<h2>Where teams get stuck</h2>
			<p>Most websites do not break all at once. They slowly drift. Plugins fall behind, forms stop working, content gets stale, links break, and no one has a clear plan for keeping the site healthy.</p>
			<p>By the time someone notices, the site is already creating friction for visitors and extra stress for the team.</p>
			<h2>How we fix it</h2>
			<p>We handle the ongoing maintenance that keeps a website usable and trustworthy: updates, backups, bug fixes, broken-link cleanup, and monitoring for issues that should be caught before they become bigger problems.</p>
			<h2>What moving forward looks like</h2>
			<p>If your site already feels neglected or your team needs a reliable partner to keep it stable after launch, we can help define a support rhythm that fits the platform and the level of urgency.</p>
			<p><a href='/contact/' class='button button--green'>Talk Through Support Needs</a></p>
		</div>
		<ServicesRelatedWork tag={82} />
	</div>
	<FeaturedArticles />
</Layout>
